This module creates all resources necessary for the Azure Security Center Workspace deployment, establishes pricing tier, and 
creates a security contact for the workspace.

Current State:  There are a number of issues/bugs with Microsoft Security Center and there are open tickets with the vendor
to address them.  

The following resources are created in this deployment:

    - Azure Security Center Workspace Deployment (Commented out)
    - Azure Security Center Pricing Tier
    - Azure Security Center Contact

Future State:  Pending bug resolution with Microsoft.

Prior to Updating this Module or Consuming Azure Security Center Resources, Please Refer to:

https://gsep.daimler.com/confluence/display/DTNATELE/Telematics+2.0+README+Reference+Document

Official Microsoft Documentation for the Azure Security Center Service:

https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/security-center/

Terraform Resources for Azure Security Center Service:

https://www.terraform.io/docs/providers/azurerm/r/security_center_workspace.html